						               													<description>A 37 card expansion for the Chaos Isle: Zombi Deck card game, Apocalypse adds a whole new deck to the game, adding tension and sense of impending chaos. Players draw a card from this deck at the start of their turn and resolve one of its five card types: Ally, Equipment, Location, Zombi or Doomsday card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Doomsday cards require one or more players to meet some criteria or the card will be added to the &amp;quot;Doomsday Track&amp;quot;. When the Doomsday Track has reached its limit based on the number of players in the game, the Apocalypse is triggered, profoundly changing the rules for the remainder of the game, often bringing about about a quick and decisive ending.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Apocalypse requires the original Chaos Isle: Zombi Deck base game to play and can be played with any other Chaos Isle expansion. Apocalypse works particularly well with the Rise of The Creator expansion.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
